-field formulation,
 detailing the practical realisation within an OctoMap-based mapping pipeline,
 including the extension from 2-D to weighted 3-D voxel chunks.
 Subsequent subsections summarise the preliminary treatment of environmental hazard layers,
 the integration of efficiency-based risk terms,
 and the initial map-fusion experiments.
 The chapter concludes with a concise statement of contributions to date and highlights the principal shortcomings and open issues that motivate the work planned for Years 2 and 3.
\end_layout

